{"tid":1571601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一路以黎 和理 同 勇武 都搵錯對手","createTime":"2019-09-15T13:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T00:51:18.000Z","uid":882,"like":148,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"6fac9cb7560bf86e1d4c5570cb59c36fdb0b096f","tid":1571601,"uid":882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:00:39.000Z","msg":"以前一路都係<br />\n勇武 對抗 犬<br />\n和理非落區俾藍絲騷擾<br />\n<br />\n結果兩邊戰線都裝備差距太大而蝕晒底<br />\n<br />\n其實應該<br />\n勇武 對 藍絲 <br />\n和理 對 犬<br />\n<br />\n大家要記住 同犬係裝備上鬥升級 係無可能既，正正係咁 我地要跳出黎諗裸裝，和理非做前線，犬傷佢地一條毛都會被國際戰線放大。<br />\n<br />\n同時間勇武既對像應該係騷擾做文宣和理非既藍絲，裝備對等，贏係士氣波黎<br />\n<br />\n咁樣條數就岩晒啦"},{"pid":"a8e809f4ea5c06405cdfeda58149683e953c073e","tid":1571601,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:02:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ddb814e9df33a4fc9bf154fe9fb051cc735b1a","tid":1571601,"uid":12447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:02:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a828a364ff3007b59c9e90f0a17e86bba27461","tid":1571601,"uid":113716,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:04:11.000Z","msg":"和理之所以和理係驚俾人拉<br />\n又點會同你對住啲狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a07005a708d43459f45b28fad0d4916ec6e6394d","tid":1571601,"uid":202706,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:06:05.000Z","msg":"唔可行<br />\n和理非見到防暴速龍即走<br />\n莫講做前線同佢地對峙<br />\n到時一定一大堆人只顧自己<br />\n冇人救人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21fc866571bc4582d9f6e159dc8be2cfa1077c5","tid":1571601,"uid":202224,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:07:39.000Z","msg":"可能第一粒tg就完左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd2b47a40848a1f2fd278e8545abe447eaec5e5","tid":1571601,"uid":20723,"like":0,"dislike